<p>Want to reduce your power bill? Solar is the perfect way to do it! <b>We can help you install solar panels and batteries in your home or business</b>, so you can start saving money right away. Our team is experienced in renewable energy systems, so you can be sure the job will be done right.</p><p><span style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; color: var( --e-global-color-secondary ); background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);">SolarState offers homeowners and business owners an affordable and high-quality solar energy system. Our solar panels are the </span><span style="font-style: inherit; color: var( --e-global-color-secondary ); background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);"><b>highest quality</b></span><span style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; color: var( --e-global-color-secondary ); background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);"> and our installers are the </span><span style="font-style: inherit; color: var( --e-global-color-secondary ); background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);"><b>best in the business</b></span><span style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; color: var( --e-global-color-secondary ); background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);">. We make it easy for you to go solar with a hassle-free installation process.</span></p><div></div>						</div>
